Notes on pseudopotentials:
 - Some analogies:
     pyscf.gto           ---   pyscf.pbc
     gto.Mole            ---   pbc.Cell
     gto/mole.py         ---   pbc/cell.py
     Mole.format_basis   ---   Cell.format_pseudo
     gto.basis           ---   pbc.pseudo
     basis.parse_nwchem  ---   pseudo.parse_cp2k
